04e0f6866212309b4fbc5d6a40fbde83e9a3ba02.query:
SELECT 
                    local_id, 
                    parent_id, 
                    intellect.id AS intellect_id
                FROM cells 
                INNER JOIN intellect
                ON cells.local_id = intellect.cell_id
                WHERE generation_id = $1 
                AND EXISTS
                (
                    SELECT * FROM diffs WHERE
                    cell_id = cells.id AND
                    tick_id <= $2 AND
                    type = 'create_cell'
                )
                AND NOT EXISTS 
                (
                    SELECT * FROM diffs WHERE 
                    cell_id = cells.id AND 
                    tick_id <= $2 AND 
                    type = 'remove_cell'
                )

70d959d98ced3162e1a70d5930c58dc395bb1d92.query:
INSERT INTO 
                diffs(cell_id, tick_id, type, changed_module, new_value) 
                SELECT id, $1, $2, evnts.module, evnts.new_value FROM 
                (SELECT * FROM UNNEST($4::INTEGER[], $5::VARCHAR[], $6::DECIMAL[]) AS DATA(local_id, module, new_value)) evnts
                INNER JOIN cells 
                ON evnts.local_id = cells.local_id 
                WHERE cells.generation_id = $3

7f7eb01e97d2aa17d1b45f7ec30d691ed7f9d8d2.query:
INSERT INTO 
                diffs(cell_id, tick_id, type) 
                SELECT id, $1, $2 FROM 
                (SELECT * FROM UNNEST($3::INTEGER[]) AS DATA(local_id)) local_ids
                INNER JOIN cells 
                ON local_ids.local_id = cells.local_id 
                WHERE cells.generation_id = $4

83c64061d778ac17714d83a9c5bbefb55facc8ae.query:
SELECT 
                        modules.name AS module_name,
                        modules.value AS initial_value,
                        (
                            SELECT 
                                new_value 
                            FROM
                                diffs 
                            WHERE 
                                tick_id <= $2 AND 
                                cell_id = $1 AND 
                                changed_module = modules.name
                            ORDER BY tick_id DESC
                            LIMIT 1
                        ) AS changed_value
                    FROM modules
                    WHERE cell_id = $1

aeb761425009fdcac87491d61da8eeace5e736af.query:
SELECT 
            map_id, life_type, feed_type, setup_type, tick_period, description, name
            FROM 
            (
                SELECT map_id, life_type, feed_type, setup_type, tick_period, description, name, usr.id
                FROM
                generations
                INNER JOIN 
                (
                    SELECT id FROM users WHERE login = $1
                ) usr
                ON generations.owner_id = usr.id 
            ) gen_usr

e6f06b5975204911ad370182b8b4d16fcfae1f45.query:
SELECT 
                    in_neuron_count, 
                    out_neuron_count,
                    (
                        SELECT ARRAY_AGG(bias::DECIMAL) FROM neurons WHERE intellect_id = $1
                    ) AS neuron_biases,
                    (
                        SELECT ARRAY_AGG(from_id::INTEGER) FROM gens WHERE intellect_id = $1
                    ) AS gen_from_ids,
                    (
                        SELECT ARRAY_AGG(to_id::INTEGER) FROM gens WHERE intellect_id = $1
                    ) AS gen_to_ids,
                    (
                        SELECT ARRAY_AGG(weight::DECIMAL) FROM gens WHERE intellect_id = $1
                    ) AS gen_weights
                FROM intellect
